{"lemma":"عَثَراتِ","slug":"عَثَراتِ","root":"ع.ث.ر","root_slug":"ع-ث-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ث-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28032","n28033"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%AB%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28032","headword_ar":"عَثْرَةٌ","root":"Evr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stumble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in walking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going along:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EavaraAtN","text_ar":"عَثَرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A slip, lapse, fault, wrong action,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mistake;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, TA;) so called as being"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fall into sin"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crime."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqaAla A@ll~`hu Eavorataka","text_ar":"اَقَالَ ا@للّٰهُ عَثْرَتَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God cancel thy slip, lapse, fault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (A.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA Haliyma A_il~aA *uw EavorapK","text_ar":"لَا حَلِيمَ اـِلَّا ذُو عَثْرَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no one"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be characterized as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a forbearing disposition except"},{"kind":"text","text":"he be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who has committed a slip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and becomes admonished thereby, distinguishing the occasions of error so as to avoid them [and to make allowance for others who have done the like]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"War,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fight, against unbelievers"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"others;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because war, or fight, is an occasion of frequent stumbling, or tripping: so in a trad., in which it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tabodaA^ohumo biAlEavorapi","text_ar":"لَا تَبْدَاْهُمْ بِالعَثْرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Begin not ye with them by war"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning invite ye them first to El-Islám or to the payment of the poll-tax; and if they assent not, then have recourse to war. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n28033","headword_ar":"عَثِرَةٌ","root":"Evr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"Land ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroD","text_ar":"اَرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without herbage, being high, and overspread with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eivoyar","text_ar":"عِثْيَر"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA:) and said to occur in a trad. as the name of a particular land. (O, K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}